sequenceDiagram
    participant Config as Configuration Phase
    participant API as Public API
    participant Parser as Dedicated Parser
    participant Meta as Metadata Prep
    participant Time as Timestamp Stabilizer
    participant Asm as Envelope Assembler
    participant Env as Final Envelope
    participant Exp as Exposure View
    participant Handoff as Handoff Contract
    participant Circ as Circulation Boundary

    Config->>Config: Resolve active profile, parser, metadata, timestamp, assembler, handoff target
    API->>Parser: Content-only input
    Parser->>Parser: Parse with configured dedicated parser
    Parser-->>Asm: Parsed content ref/view
    Meta-->>Asm: Prepared metadata block
    Time-->>Asm: Stabilized timestamp
    Asm->>Env: Compose final envelope
    Env->>Exp: Build readiness/exposure view
    Exp->>Handoff: Submit ready exposure
    Handoff-->>Circ: Contract-ready admission candidate
    Note over Circ: Circulation internals are out of LogAPI scope
